sequenceDiagram
  participant User as ユーザー
  participant AgentLoop as Agent Loop
  participant Model as Model
  participant Runtime as Runtime
  participant Tool as Tool Executor
  participant Log as Event Log

  User->>AgentLoop: 失敗テストを修正する
  AgentLoop->>Model: 現在の context
  Model-->>AgentLoop: tool intent: bash npm test
  AgentLoop->>Runtime: validate intent
  Runtime->>Runtime: permission decision
  Runtime->>Log: record intent + decision
  Runtime->>Tool: execute command
  Tool-->>Runtime: exitCode + output + artifacts
  Runtime->>Log: record execution event
  Runtime-->>AgentLoop: observation projection
  AgentLoop->>Model: 次ターンの context に observation を含める
